t February 22, 2020, PASSOS sent a series of text messages to Individual 2 =
that said, in sum and substance, =E2=80=9CI will spread this story that ber=
k [i.e., Berkshire Hathaway] bought 28 MM of shares.=E2=80=9D PASSOS added =
=E2=80=9Cthen it becomes true.=E2=80=9DNo it doesn=E2=80=99t!
