 style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And in each of those cases, in hindsight it will=
 be clear that the poison pill was good and that the board=E2=80=99s effort=
s to slow Musk down were in the best interests of shareholders. In Scenario=
 1, the poison pill flushed out the fact that Musk=E2=80=99s offer was vapo=
